sampleCode:
When calling this cloud function from the Mini Program side, the code parameter must be passed in.: 

```javascript
wx.cloud
  .callFunction({
    name: 'get-phoneNumber',
    data: {
      code: event.detail.code, // Obtain from getPhoneNumber button event
    },
  })
  .then((res) => {
    console.log('MobilePhone Number: ', res.result);
  })
  .catch((err) => {
    console.error('Get MobilePhone Failed: ', err);
  });
```

This will output an object with the following structure in the debugger: 

```json
{
  "errcode": 0,
  "errmsg": "ok",
  "phone_info": {
    "phoneNumber": "xxxxxx",
    "purePhoneNumber": "xxxxxx",
    "countryCode": 86,
    "watermark": {
      "timestamp": 1637744274,
      "appid": "xxxx"
    }
  }
}
```

Notes: 

1. Required: Activate the "Get Phone Number" feature in WeChat Mini Program Admin Console
2. Install latest wx-server-sdk
3. The code can only be used once and is valid for 5 minutes.
